# Generated client (Kubb) and route tree (TanStack Router) are committed —
# they're checked in so a fresh clone can typecheck and build without first
# running codegen. Regenerate with `pnpm generate:api` and `vite dev` (the
# router plugin rewrites routeTree.gen.ts on dev start).
